(408, '5a0d59a9e914587ec1459603', 'GO', 'Futuroscope - Poitier (86) SAISON 2017 - E\'billet', 'Futuroscope', 'Location: JAUNAY CLAN Futuroscope saison 2017 Opening of the Park: from 04 February 2017 to 07 January 2018. Ticket valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. Child rate: from 5 to 16 inclusive. Free for children under 5 years. Ticket 1 day: Adult 39 € instead of 48 € Child 33 € instead of 40 € Ticket 2 consecutive days: Adult 76 € instead of 88 € Children 63 € instead of 74 € Immerse yourself in the fun, festive atmosphere family of Futuroscope! Exciting adventures, extreme sensations, fascinating live shows, night aquafeerie, captivating attractions ... There is something for every taste and every age! NEW in 2016, put on your beast skin, come and laugh and shiver family with the heroes of The Ice Age, the attraction in a totally frosted 4D adventure! Share the adventures of Sid and his friends as if you were there. Effects in the room, dynamic platform and laughter are on the program ... At nightfall, enjoy a magical evening with La Forge aux Etoiles, the new night aquafeerie imagined by the Cirque du Soleil (every evening included in the ticket price ). And still not to be missed: The Time Traveling Machine with the Raving Rabbids and Arthur, the 4D adventure, both of which are rewarded with the &quot;Best Attraction in the World&quot; award. You can not imagine what awaits you. Free-time tickets are valid for 1 day or 2 consecutive days depending on the ticket chosen from 04 February 2017 to 07 January 2018 inclusive and give unlimited access to the Futuroscope attractions (except for certain activities and paying events) one day or two consecutive days depending on the opening schedule of the Park. They also allow to attend the Nocturne Spectacle presented the very evening of the visit. The night show may be modified, delayed or canceled without prior notice for weather or technical reasons.', 'Lieu : JAUNAY CLAN\r\nFuturoscope saison 2017\r\nOuverture du Parc : du 04 février 2017 au 07 janvier 2018.\r\n\r\nBillet valable 1 an à partir de la date d\'achat.\r\nTarif enfant : de 5 à 16 inclus.\r\nGratuit pour les enfants de moins de 5 ans.\r\n\r\nBillet 1 jour :\r\nAdulte 39  au lieu de 48 \r\nEnfant 33  au lieu de 40 \r\n\r\nBillet 2 jours consécutifs :\r\nAdulte 76  au lieu de 88 \r\nEnfant 63  au lieu de 74 \r\n\r\nPlongez dans latmosphère fun, festive et familiale du Futuroscope ! \r\nAventures palpitantes, sensations extrêmes, spectacles vivants fascinants, aquaféerie nocturne, attractions captivantes INSERT INTO `eyca_quality` (`discount_id`, `eyca_id`, `CATEGORIES`, `NAME`, `VENDOR`, `DESCRIPTION_ENG`, `DESCRIPTION_LOCAL`, `EMAIL`, `PHONE`, `WEB`, `STREET`, `CITY`, `ZIP`, `COUNTRY`, `REGION`, `GEO`, `TAGS`, `IMAGE`, `PRIX`, `last_touch`) VALUES
(416, '5a0d59aae914587ec145960a', 'GO', 'SPEEDPARK - Complexes multi-activités', 'SPEEDPARK ', 'Multi-activity complexes dedicated to the whole family! New concept of indoor leisure parks grouping the following activities and different according to the sites: karting, bowling, laser, mini golf, billiard room, video games. Each ticket gives the right to an activity to choose between karting, bowling, laser or mini-golf. Tickets are valid on all establishments, every day. Due to the busy weekend, we ask you to check in before 8 pm on Fridays, Saturdays and bank holidays. Activities should be completed no later than 9 pm. Good to know : . On the Conflans-Sainte Honorine site, Les Clayes sous Bois and Beauvais, a pass card is compulsory. Its cost is 2.50 euros per year and is valid for 1 year. . Bowling is available for bowling (between 1,60 € and 1,80 € depending on the venue) - This ticket is not valid for video games. Karting (10-minute sessions), children from 7 years old and upwards of 1m30 (100 people) cm3), 14 years for adults (200 cm3), that is to say that they never turn at the same time as the adults Mini-golf: two courses for all with small club for the children - Billiards: 1 - Speedpark - Activities: bowling 30 tracks, go-karting, laser, billiards, video games Jaux (60) near Compiègne - Karting Bowling Laser: Activities: karting track on 3 levels, bowling 24 tracks, 1 stargate laser, a room of j they have videos, 15 billiards, 1 seminar room and 1 bar. Conflans-Sainte-Honorine (78) near Cergy-Pontoise - Karting Bowling Laser - Activities: kart track on the floor, bowling 40 tracks, 1 stargate laser, 1 mini golf course, 30 billiards, a seminar room and a bar. Hénin Beaumont (62) near Lille - Speedpark - Activities: kart track on 3 levels, bowling 32 tracks, 1 stargate laser, an arcade, 25 billiards, a seminar room and a bar. Blois (41) - Bowling World - Activities: bowling 20 tracks, video arcade, 15 billiards and a bar Arras (62) - Bowling World - Activitie