(566, '5a0d59c2e914587ec1459666', 'GO', 'Centre aquatique Atoo-O - Hochfelden  (67)', 'Centre aquatique Atoo-O - Hochfelden', 'Hochfelden (67) The Aquatic Center includes: A sports pool: The basin has a length of 25 meters and has 4 water lines. The depth increases gradually from 0.80 m in shallow depth to 2.10 m in deep depth. The average temperature of this basin is 28 °. The sunroof allows the sun to enter. A play pool: The play pool with a capacity of 130 m3, offers an ideal temperature of 29 °. The depth of 1,30 meters makes it a privileged space for games between children and with family. In addition, several sets of water and a bank of bubbles and massaging jets come to enhance the pool. A paddling pool: This shallow pool with its water at 29 °, is reserved for &quot;tiny ones&quot;. A small slide and jets of water will delight the most courageous of them. A toboggan: Of a length of 40 meters, it is accessible to all for the joys of the glide. A green space: Accessible in summer, the green space has loungers and a picnic area. These numerous shaded areas will be perfect to spend unforgettable moments in family. The Form Space of the Aquatic Center Atoo-o The Space Shape is a universe reserved for adults. You will find: 1 Sauna with a capacity of 4 people (swimsuit and bath towel required) 1 Hammam for 6 people 1 Sport room 1 Relaxation area with relaxation chairs', 'Hochfelden (67)\r\n\r\nLe Centre Aquatique comprend :\r\n\r\nUn bassin sportif : \r\n\r\n\r\nD’une longueur de 25 mètres ce bassin dispose de 4 lignes d’eau. La profondeur augmente progressivement passant de 0,80 m en petite profondeur à 2,10 m en grande profondeur.\r\n\r\n\r\nLa température moyenne de ce bassin est à 28°.\r\n\r\nLe toit ouvrant permet de laisser entrer le soleil.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nUn bassin ludique :\r\n\r\n\r\nLe bassin ludique d’une capacité de 130 m3, offre une température idéale de 29°. La profondeur de 1,30 mètres en fait un espace privilégié pour les jeux entre enfants et en f