(714, '5a0d5ca1e914587ec1459893', 'GO', 'Beauval Box - Saint Aignan (41)', 'Beauval Box - Saint Aignan', 'Give an original and exotic gift: a BeauvalBox, the box with everything in it! Validity: 1 year from your first call to Beauval. Beauval Zoo - St Aignan, only 2h15 from Paris! Open every day of the year, from 9am to dusk. Accessible to people with reduced mobility. Possibility of lunch on site. Shop. La Beauval Box Dispatch includes: - night in a Club room - dinners without drinks (only in low season) - buffet breakfasts - entrance to the Beauval Zoo for two consecutive days The Beauval Box Dispatch Zen includes: - night in a Club room - dinners without drinks (only in low season) - buffet breakfasts - admission to the Beauval Zoo for two consecutive days - access to the aqua relaxation area for two adults - one hour for an adult or two 30-minute treatments for two adults Validity: 1 year from your first call to Beauval. The hotel: Les Jardins de Beauval 3 * Discover all the charm of the Jardins de Beauval, a Balinese hotel *** in the heart of the Loire Valley. You will appreciate the decoration coming entirely from the islands of Bali and Java: furniture in teak plantation, sumptuously carved wooden doors, stone walls ... Heated outdoor pool, olive and palm garden, duck pond multicolour completes the scenery of your stay. The ZooParc To make this unique moment, you will discover the 4000 animals of the ZooParc de Beauval in the heart of a zoo that is highly regarded by its visitors and ranked among the most beautiful in the world by Forbes traveler. Rare and unique species in France, white tigers, okapis, koalas, manatees, etc., will delight young and old ... Enjoy! How to get there: By road: 2h15 from Paris by the A10, A71 and A85: Paris, Orléans and then Vierzon, Tours. Exit N ° 12 St Aignan. Follow Zoo directions. By train: TGV station St Pierre-des-Corps (1/2 hour from Beauval by the A 85). Train station of St Aignan - Noyers-sur-cher (8 kms). Delivery info