(988, '5a0d5a05e914587ec145975d', 'GO', 'Parc Aventure la Gataudière - Marennes (17)', 'Parc Aventure la Gataudière - Marennes', 'Marennes (17) Located in the magnificent park of the Château de la Gataudière in Marennes, you will spend a strong day in sensations in an unforgettable setting, where you will find: CHÂTEAUBRANCHE: From 3 years: start with qualified instructors for 3 hours of adventure in the heart of the forest. From the turquoise course to 1 meter high to the super black course up to 14 meters high there is for all ages! In addition to the 200 meter super zip line, two new zip lines are specially designed for children. Climbing walls, parrot ladder, trampoline and picnic areas will allow you to spend a memorable family day. PAINTBALL: From 12 years old: Supervised by a professional instructor, you will be able to play on 7 paint terrains, semi automatic launchers, protections provided, complete framing ... Covered areas, palette &amp; tires, natural wood, speed ball, maze, sab and BIG GAMES ... Fort with floor + tower of attack, forts, mini fortin and trenches ... UNFORGETTABLE ... QUADS: From 10 years (90cc) and adult from 14 years (150cc): Challenge your friends on a closed track of 650 meters, in sand, with turned corners. BUBBLE FOOT: Play protected football in a bubble, is played by teams of 4 or 5 people / 30 minutes. 05 46 85 01 07', 'Marennes (17)\r\nSitué dans le magnifique parc du Château de la Gataudière à Marennes, Venez passer une journée forte en sensations dans un cadre inoubliable, où vous trouverez :&nbsp;\r\nCHÂTEAUBRANCHE :&nbsp;À partir de 3 ans : lancez-vous avec des moniteurs qualifiés pour 3 heures d’aventure au coeur de la forêt.&nbsp;Du parcours turquoise à 1 mètre de haut au parcours super noir allant jusqu’à 14 mètres de haut il y en a pour tous les âges !&nbsp;En complément de la super tyrolienne de 200 mètres, 2 nouvelles tyroliennes spécialement conçues pour les enfants.&nbsp;Murs d’escalade, échelle de perroquet, trampoli