(1345, '5a0d5cc4e914587ec14599dc', 'HB', 'Spa Villa Thalgo - Paris (75)', 'Spa Villa Thalgo - Paris ', 'Villa Thalgo is like a refuge from the Parisian tumult and in our lives in perpetual movement. We wanted it so: both serenity bubble to deeply recharge you and form space to stimulate and enrich your energy. Our demand, of course, is due to the THALGO expertise and their powerful assets drawn from the heart of the oceans, but not only ... We believe that nothing is worth the human contact, the one that privileges listening, touch, accompaniment. This &quot;humanist&quot; philosophy is definitely ours, and all the actors of the THALGO VILLA - hostesses, spa practitioners, sports coaches and governesses - have the same ambition: to welcome you, to listen to you and to make you benefit from their know-how, to finally make you love the VILLA THALGO, as much as we love it. Aquatic space: In the heart of the VILLA THALGO, the sports pool gives the star to the aquatic activities. Aqua-training, Aqua-biking ... 56 classes per week that make our fame on these easily addictive activities. Without forgetting the relaxation: our hydro-massage course under lights and giant screen has also been imagined to transport you instantly in a marine environment exotic and deeply relaxing.Grand Hammam Marin: The Grand Hammam Marin is the image of the VILLA THALGO: refined, elegant and entirely turned towards the marine universe. With its water vapor enriched with mineral salts, this exclusive concept takes you deeply, like after a day spent by the ocean. Its refreshing central pool ends up transforming this ancestral ritual into a particularly exotic marine experience.Fitness: The fitness area of ​​the VILLA THALGO is a place that one would like to keep for oneself: intimate, sheltered from the looks.Cut Sensory ( Cabins): Our treatment rooms are comfortable, elegant and quiet. Of course, you will relax more than anywhere else. But again, magic will work mainly through the mastery and p