(546, '5a0d5c9be914587ec1459854', 'GO', 'Forum de Tregastel Piscine (22)', 'Forum de Tregastel Piscine', 'Tregastel (22) The Forum de Tregastel, located in front of the beach of Coz Pors in Trégastel, welcomes you for a moment of relaxation, sport or fitness: Treat yourself to the benefits of sea water in relaxing in the large saltwater pool at 30 ° C with a light current, massaging jets and bubbling benches. In addition to the main swimming pool, you will enjoy the pleasures of relaxation with the equipment inspired by the thermal baths of Antiquity and complemented by the most modern technologies: Hammam, sauna, jacuzzi, relaxation room. Finally, the cardio-fitness room is equipped with numerous cardio-training machines and guided machines to sculpt your body: bikes, rowers, ellipticals, shopping mats Attention The bathing cap is obligatory (on sale at the reception at 2 , 50 €), Bathing shorts are forbidden, only boxers and bathing towels are allowed, Child rate: our rate is valid only during the school holidays, otherwise take the entrance to 3.10 € directly at the reception all days outside school holidays. Opening hours during school holidays: Monday: 14h00-19h30. Tuesday and Thursday: 10.00-13.00 and 15.00-21.00 Wednesday: 10.00-13.00 and 15.00-19.30 Saturday: 10.00-13.00 and 15.00-18.30 Sunday and public holidays: 10.00-18.30 Opening hours during the school holidays: Monday and Wednesday: 10h00-19h30 Tuesday, Thursday and Friday: 10h00-21h00 Saturday, Sunday and public holidays: 10h00-18h30', 'Tregastel (22) \r\n\r\nLe Forum de  Tregastel, situé face à la plage du Coz Pors en Trégastel, vous accueille pour un moment de détente, de sport ou de remise en forme :Offrez-vous les bienfaits de l\'eau de mer en vous détendant dans la grande piscine d\'eau de mer à 30°C agrémentée d\'un léger courant, de jets massants et de banquettes bouillonnantes. Outre la piscine principale, vous gouterez aux plaisirs de la relaxation avec les équipements inspirés des thermes de